 No Man 's Land Fort , a Victorian sea fort in the middle of the Solent , is set to open this month .
The isolated fort , one of three guarding the entrance to the Isle of Wight has been turned into a rooftop hot tub , shops and even its own nightclub .
The No Mans Fort has been transformed by AmaZing Venues to become a luxury hotel , and is to open on April 23 .